Justin Herwick https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Justin_Herwick 0 Justin Herwick (born June 27, 1970) is an American former actor. He is best known for his role as Jackson in Everett Lewis's 2002 film Luster.Herwick was married to actor Nicole Eggert from 2000 to 2002. They have a daughter together, born in 1998.
